- rule_name: ledger_seconds
  severity: Warning
  message: "Ledger sequence number mixed with a seconds-magnitude literal `86400`; sequence numbers count blocks (~5s each), not seconds"
  location: "deadline:18"
  suggestion: "Use `env.ledger().timestamp()` for time windows measured in seconds, or convert the duration to a ledger count before adding it to `sequence()`"
